snippet.title: Symphony of War - Official Legends DLC Teaser Trailer | Publisher Spotlight Showcase 2023
snippet.description: Watch the latest trailer for Symphony of War to see what to expect with the upcoming Legends DLC, which brings 8 new characters, a new army, 13 unit classes, New Game+, and more to the 2D Turn-based Strategy RPG.
